Story
Once upon a time there lived a monkey in a forest who resided on a mango tree which was on a bank of a river.
In the same forest lived a crocodile and his wife.One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.The kind hearted monkey saw the crocodile and offered him some fruits.
The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them.As days passed by the crocodile and the monkey became goood friends.
The monkey offered fruits for crocodile's wife and she tasted the fruits and she felt how tasty they are,so how the money's heart would be.